<br>
I abhor terrorism, but just because the bad guys fight dirty doesn't mean we have to.  Detaining thousands of muslim-americans and trying suspected in military courts is not what I call democracy.  I firmly believe terrorism has to be rooted out and stopped, but not by illegal holdings and interogation.  What's next, a steady erosion of other rights?<br>
